<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9fafb;
      }
      .tip-box {
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        background-color: white;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4f46e5;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #6b7280;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Time to Practice!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</h2>
      <p>
        It's been a while since your last language practice session. Regular practice is key to improving your language skills!
      </p>
      
      <div class="tip-box">
        <h3>Today's Language Tip</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Consistency matters more than duration.</strong> Even just 10 minutes of focused practice each day can lead to significant improvements over time.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <p>
        Ready to practice? Try one of these activities:
      </p>
      
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Record a short speech</strong> and get feedback on your pronunciation</li>
        <li><strong>Have a conversation</strong> with our AI language partners</li>
        <li><strong>Review your past sessions</strong> to track your improvement</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="<%= @url %>" class="button">Start Practicing Now</a>
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Happy learning!<br>
        The Flukebase Team
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Flukebase. All rights reserved.<br>
        You're receiving this email because you opted in to practice reminders.
        <br>
        <a href="<%= profile_url %>">Update your notification preferences</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
